The way I would test this is by optionally injecting a tear-off Process.runSync, for example:

```
typedef ProcessRunSync = ProcessResult Function(String, List<String>, ...more stuff)

class Cocoon {
  Cocoon({..., @visibleForTesting this.processRunSync = Process.runSync }) ;

   final ProcessRunSync processRunSync;

}
```

Then you can provide your own callback for testing that returns an example output you observed.

